= Related Works

== Decentralized web querying

Multiple efforts have been made to render this information machine understandable to enable automated agent to power diverse applications.
Early example of such approach is webSQL @Mendelzon1996 that enable query engine to capture decentralized web information using conjunctive queries.
The data retrieve by WebSQL is not web friendly as it does not provide sufficient context to interlink it with multiple sources furthermore it is necessary to make
decentralized queries to maintain web indexes.

